# FST outlier and PCA per Chromosome
All the FST outlier plots are using Lynn Canal as the focal population. 


![](../figures/fst/LynnCanal_Chr_1plot_fst.jpg)  
![](../figures/pcas/chrom1_pca-byChrom.jpg)  

**Conclusion**: Nothing very interesting. A small island shared between Pervenets, AI pops and Unimak (some Shumagians).

![](../figures/fst/LynnCanal_Chr_2plot_fst.jpg)  
![](../figures/pcas/chrom2_pca-byChrom.jpg)  

**Conclusion**: Nothing very interesting. Very small island at the start that is shared between wGOA, AI and some Pervenets. Some genomewide differentiation between AI/Bering Sea/Unimak and GOA

![](../figures/fst/LynnCanal_Chr_3plot_fst.jpg)  
![](../figures/pcas/chrom3_pca-byChrom.jpg)  

**Conclusion**: AI island towards the middle of the chromosome (ADD BASES).
